# Recommended Certifications

After gaining practical experience, consider:

* AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner
* AWS Certified Solutions Architect – Associate
* AWS Certified Developer – Associate
* AWS Certified SysOps Administrator – Associate
* AWS Certified Security – Specialty
* Certified Kubernetes Application Developer (CKAD)
* Certified Kubernetes Administrator (CKA)

# Learning Order

1. Linux
2. Networking
3. Python
4. Git & GitHub
5. SQL
6. FastAPI
7. Docker
8. Kubernetes
9. AWS
10. Terraform
11. CI/CD
12. Monitoring
13. Cloud Security
14. Serverless
15. Advanced Cloud Architecture

Following this roadmap will prepare you to deploy and operate production-ready systems and will directly support building scalable products like **XSOLA**, while also providing a strong foundation for cloud engineering and DevOps roles.





































